data.text: I want all of America to denounce you. I want you impeached. I want you gone. I want your repugnant party gone. Your administration is made up of Greedy Old Perverts who are more evil than Satan. If you drink you’re swamped it would be empty. Empty like you’re brainless head.

If the end of the world is coming I want to see you go first before I do. The way you treat all that is good and right with this country and its people is so disgusting there are no words. I wish Mueller to find you guilty of federal crimes. I want you in jail bending over.

You are a liar, cheat, thief, sexual deviant, narcissistic sociopath. I am a person who has always had a good heart yet I wish ill on you every day of my life. I pray ill on you every day of my life. I hear your voice and I puke. I see your face and I puke again.
